data.description: Welcome to this charming and well-appointed rowhouse, just a short distance  from 'Canton Square.' This updated home features a spacious living room and dining area with open riser stairs, perfect for entertaining. The gourmet kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a wine rack. Off the kitchen is a bonus room, ideal for a breakfast room or office, with a slider to the beautifully landscaped backyard patio. Upstairs, you'll find two roomy bedrooms and two baths, including an ensuite. The convenience of a laundry area on the second level adds to the functionality of this home. Picture yourself living close to Canton's vibrant shopping, entertainment, and dining scene. This home is convenient to everything with its close proximity to Canton Square, Baltimore Harbor, Canton Waterfront Park, the Harbor Connector stop, bus stops, I-695,  I-95, I-895, and so much more!  Schedule a viewing today and envision yourself calling this delightful space your own!  Offer Deadline Monday 4/15/24 10 am
